-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                             May this be love - Jimi Hendrix
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
incredibly awesome song.
I didn't like the other tab for this so i decided to take the time.
you want to let the low and high Eb ring through the whole verse.
i didn't bother with the second or third verse(only "slightly" different) , or the 
solo (other tab on here has it)


Tuning:Eb Bb Gb Db Ab Eb

